item.title: The Chipmunks & The Chipettes - Party Rock Anthem
item.description:
For Educational Use.
Lowered 4 semitones for beginner ukulele. From the movie "Alvin and the Chipmunks 3 - Shipwrecked”.
If you found this video useful please subscribe and share with your friends. If you want to be notified of future videos please click on bell next to subscribe.
